WESTERN SOUTH ATLANTIC.
URUGUAY.
1. SEISMIC SURVEY 01 AND 02 AUG BY M/V RAMFORM VANGUARD
   TOWING 12 7000 METER LONG CABLES ALONG TRACKLINES BETWEEN:
   A. 34-32.33S 052-16.63W AND 35-12.22S 051-14.32W.
   B. 35-15.85S 051-20.90W AND 34-35.90S 052-23.22W.
   NINE MILE BERTH REQUESTED.
2. CANCEL HYDROLANT 1849/13.
3. CANCEL THIS MSG 03 AUG 13.
